QuestData.Title: Explorers' League Document (5 of 6)
QuestData.Description: The document bears the Explorers' League crest and contains a detailed list of the artifacts excavated by Ironband's workers in southeastern Loch Modan. Sooty smudges lead you to believe it was likely stolen by the Dark Iron spies in the area.$B$BYou recall mention of missing documents at the Explorers' League building in Thelsamar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Explorers' League Document to Torren Squarejaw in Thelsamar.
QuestData.RewardText: Our artifact records! I was pretty well worried what the Dark Irons might try to steal with this information at their disposal.$B$BThank you for bringing this back to us. We'll gladly part with some coin to express our gratitude.
